# data/lighthouse-results.json — committed as empty [] so AUD-013/AUD-034 have a
# file to read in Phase 1; plan 11's persist-lhci.mjs overwrites with real data
# after each `pnpm lhci` run. The freshly-written copy is gitignored via the
# explicit pattern below ONLY when working-tree diff is purely numeric drift —
# baseline JSON tracking is intentional (see Open Question 8 in 1-RESEARCH.md).
data/quality-gate-pass.md
data/quality-gate-failure.md
# NER scan output — regenerated by `pnpm qa:ner` (plan 09)
data/ner-results.json
# Plan 10: axe-core + IS-5568 a11y wrapper output (ephemeral)
data/axe-results.json
data/a11y-il-results.json

